   Local Interest
     __________________________________________________________________

NSSL Community . . .

     NSSL is an integral part of a larger weather community in the
     Norman, Oklahoma area comprised of government and academic research
     agencies that share resources, interests, and activities. NSSL is
     committed to community involvement through activities such as the
     United Way "Day of Caring," the Combined Federal Campaign, an annual
     Open House, and educational outreach through schools and business
     organizations.
